dct_title_s: Nova tabula geographica complectens Borealiorem Americæ partem : in qua exacte delineatæ sunt Canada sive Nova Francia, Nova Scotia, Nova Anglia, Novum Belgium, Pensylvania, Virginia, Carolina, et Terra Nova : cum omnibus littorum, pulvinorumque profunditatibus
dct_description_sm: Shows part of eastern north America; relief shown pictorially; depths shown by soundings. "Cum privilegio ordinum generalium Fœderati Belgii."
